One delivery issue is now clear: the PNG is 3520×1920 (the expected raster size for 11×6 inches at 320), but it contains no physical-resolution chunk; system inspection reports 72 dpi/undefined units. I’m treating the explicit “300+ dpi” acceptance requirement as unmet rather than inferring it from the script.
